beer.beer_description: Revel’s Browntown American Brown Ale pours a deep amber brown with a toasty warmth and smooth rich flavour.  In true Revel fashion we’ve loaded this this one up with US flavoured hops; Cascade, Amarillo, & Williamette to provide a fruity & piney aroma with plenty of bitterness to balance out the malty  body. One to be savoured!
